{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Create a custom full-width promotional banner section for the customer account portal page (Recharge portal context).
    
    Design requirements:
    
    * Clean, premium layout aligned with Mystery Tackle Box brand
    * Background: light beige/off-white (#F5EFE6 or similar)
    * Typography: bold, uppercase headings with strong hierarchy
    * Primary colors: deep green (#2F5D57) and brown (#8B6B4A)
    * Maintain high contrast and readability
    
    Section structure:
    
    * Full-width container (no boxed layout)
    * Left side: promotional image (uploaded asset: MTB Rev Ups banner)
    * Right side: content block
    
    Content:
    
    * Headline: “REV UPS”
    * Subheadline: “Free access to the best fishing apps just for being a subscriber”
    * CTA button: “Learn More”
    * CTA style: rounded button, orange or brand accent color, strong visibility
    
    Behavior:
    
    * Fully responsive (stack image on top for mobile)
    * Maintain spacing consistency with portal UI
    * Do not override or break existing Recharge portal components
    
    Technical:
    
    * Section must be compatible with Shopify theme editor
    * No external dependencies
    * Optimize image for fast loading
    * Allow easy content editing (text + image + CTA link)
    
    Goal:
    Enhance engagement inside the customer portal and highlight subscriber perks without disrupting the existing UX.
    , I don't want any tet in the section i want to be adjusted only for the iamge , Create a custom promotional banner section for the customer account portal (Recharge portal).
    
    Design goal:
    Match the exact layout shown in the reference: a clean, full-width promotional banner with no boxed container, aligned with Mystery Tackle Box brand.
    
    Layout:
    
    * Full-width section (edge-to-edge, no max-width container)
    * No shadows, no cards, no borders
    * Tight vertical spacing (compact like portal UI)
    
    Images:
    
    * Support TWO separate images:
    
      1. Desktop image (wide banner)
      2. Mobile image (optimized vertical/stacked version)
    * Desktop: show only desktop image
    * Mobile: show only mobile image
    * Use CSS media queries (not JS) to switch visibility
    * Ensure images are responsive and not distorted
    
    Content behavior:
    
    * Entire banner should be clickable (CTA link)
    * Optional overlay support (but default = image-only like reference)
    * No text duplication if image already contains text
    
    Brand styling:
    
    * Colors: deep green (#2F5D57), brown (#8B6B4A), light beige background
    * Clean, premium, minimal design
    * No extra padding that breaks alignment with portal sections
    
    Technical requirements:
    
    * Section must be Shopify theme editor compatible
    * Allow separate upload fields:
    
      * Desktop image picker
      * Mobile image picker
      * CTA link
    * Use lazy loading for images
    * Maintain fast performance
    
    Responsiveness:
    
    * Desktop: full-width horizontal banner
    * Mobile: stacked/optimized image, full width
    * Maintain aspect ratio per device
    
    Constraints:
    
    * Do NOT use a single image for all devices
    * Do NOT center inside a container
    * Do NOT add extra text blocks unless specified
    * Do NOT override Recharge portal styles
    
    Goal:
    Deliver a high-converting promotional banner inside the customer portal with full control over desktop vs mobile experience.
    
{% enddoc %}

{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
  .ai-portal-banner-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.background_color }};
    padding: {{ block.settings.vertical_spacing_mobile }}px 0;
  }

  .ai-portal-banner-link-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    text-decoration: none;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .ai-portal-banner-link-{{ ai_gen_id }}:not([href]) {
    cursor: default;
  }

  .ai-portal-banner-image-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    position: relative;
  }

  .ai-portal-banner-desktop-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: none;
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
  }

  .ai-portal-banner-mobile-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
  }

  .ai-portal-banner-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
    background-color: #F5EFE6;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    position: relative;
  }

  .ai-portal-banner-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }} svg {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    opacity: 0.2;
  }

  .ai-portal-banner-empty-state-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 20px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    padding: 12px 24px;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #8B6B4A;
    text-align: center;
    pointer-events: none;
    background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    border-radius: 4px;
  }

  @media screen and (min-width: 750px) {
    .ai-portal-banner-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: {{ block.settings.vertical_spacing_desktop }}px 0;
    }

    .ai-portal-banner-desktop-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      display: block;
    }

    .ai-portal-banner-mobile-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      display: none;
    }

    .ai-portal-banner-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      aspect-ratio: 21 / 9;
    }
  }
{% endstyle %}

<div class="ai-portal-banner-{{ ai_gen_id }}" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
  {% if block.settings.cta_link != blank %}
    <a href="{{ block.settings.cta_link }}" class="ai-portal-banner-link-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
  {% else %}
    <div class="ai-portal-banner-link-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
  {% endif %}
    
    <div class="ai-portal-banner-image-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
      {% if block.settings.desktop_image or block.settings.mobile_image %}
        {% if block.settings.desktop_image %}
          <img
            src="{{ block.settings.desktop_image | image_url: width: 2400 }}"
            alt="{{ block.settings.desktop_image.alt | escape }}"
            loading="lazy"
            width="{{ block.settings.desktop_image.width }}"
            height="{{ block.settings.desktop_image.height }}"
            class="ai-portal-banner-desktop-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
          >
        {% endif %}
        
        {% if block.settings.mobile_image %}
          <img
            src="{{ block.settings.mobile_image | image_url: width: 1200 }}"
            alt="{{ block.settings.mobile_image.alt | escape }}"
            loading="lazy"
            width="{{ block.settings.mobile_image.width }}"
            height="{{ block.settings.mobile_image.height }}"
            class="ai-portal-banner-mobile-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
          >
        {% endif %}
      {% else %}
        <div class="ai-portal-banner-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          {{ 'image' | placeholder_svg_tag }}
          <div class="ai-portal-banner-empty-state-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            Add desktop and mobile banner images
          </div>
        </div>
      {% endif %}
    </div>
  
  {% if block.settings.cta_link != blank %}
    </a>
  {% else %}
    </div>
  {% endif %}
</div>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Portal promo banner",
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Images"
    },
    {
      "type": "image_picker",
      "id": "desktop_image",
      "label": "Desktop banner image",
      "info": "Recommended: 2400x900px or wider horizontal format"
    },
    {
      "type": "image_picker",
      "id": "mobile_image",
      "label": "Mobile banner image",
      "info": "Recommended: 800x1000px or optimized vertical format"
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Link"
    },
    {
      "type": "url",
      "id": "cta_link",
      "label": "Banner link",
      "info": "Makes entire banner clickable"
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Spacing"
    },
    {
      "type": "range",
      "id": "vertical_spacing_mobile",
      "label": "Mobile vertical spacing",
      "min": 0,
      "max": 60,
      "step": 5,
      "unit": "px",
      "default": 15
    },
    {
      "type": "range",
      "id": "vertical_spacing_desktop",
      "label": "Desktop vertical spacing",
      "min": 0,
      "max": 80,
      "step": 5,
      "unit": "px",
      "default": 20
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Background"
    },
    {
      "type": "color",
      "id": "background_color",
      "label": "Background color",
      "default": "#F5EFE6"
    }
  ],
  "presets": [
    {
      "name": "Portal promo banner"
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
